page.title: 20 FURTHER EVENTS AND PLACES
page.content:
The area contains 1st Shiplake Scout Group, whose headquarters are situated in Shiplake Rise, opposite the White Heart. The group was formed sixty years ago. HOUSING: The area contains a mixture of old and new housing and the restoration of the older houses has attracted many commuters to the village who have tried to create an atmosphere separate to that of their working conditions.
DOOMSDAY PROJECT WORK BY RICHARD TOWNHILL & PETER GRENVILLE with thanks to other college students who gave us their time and local knowledge. July 1985.
